# 2048 Command Line GAME

Implementation of the famous 2048 mobile game, using the ncurses library.

## Plug & play

Use the makefile to install the ncurses library and compile the source file.
Now it's ready to go!

## Usage

Use the arrow keys to navigate the menu and play the game.

It has the options to start a new game, resume the last one where you left of, 
if you exited by pressing 'q', see the heighscores (kept in a .txt file) and 
quit the application.